Using @echrec data to look at Blast Zone out of War of the Spark shows that the turn you play it you can destroy the following:

0/20 Most popular commanders of all time
0/100 planeswalkers
9/100 enchantments
9/100 artifacts
10/100 creatures
If you don't use it and you instead spend 2 mana to add a counter you can hit:

0/20 Most popular commanders of all time
2/100 planeswalkers
12/100 enchantments
25/100 artifacts
12/100 creatures
And if you instead spend 4 mana to get up to 3 counters you can destroy:

3/20 Most popular commanders of all time
12/100 planeswalkers
36/100 enchantments
25/100 artifacts
17/100 creatures

So between using it that turn, spending 2, or spending 4 mana to pump it you can hit the following depending on what you pick:

3/20 Most popular commanders of all time
14/100 planeswalkers
57/100 enchantments
59/100 artifacts
39/100 creatures
